These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
House: cape-cod, farmhouse
Transport: tram, jet-ski
1. Transport:tram is in an even position##4
2. Transport:jet-ski == House:farmhouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| House   | farmhouse | cape-cod |
| Transport     | jet-ski    | tram   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: sports, scientific
Pet: guinea-pig, lizard
1. Pet:guinea-pig is in an odd position##4
2. Movie-Genre:scientific is on the left of Movie-Genre:sports##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | sports        |
| Pet      | guinea-pig  | lizard |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Game: canasta, go
Food: kale, mango
1. Food:kale is in an odd position##4
2. Game:go is on the left of Game:canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Game   | go    | canasta |
| Food   | kale | mango |

